44:06.360 --> 44:08.880
    # It's really not his brain

44:08.880 --> 44:12.880
      # That makes me thrill

44:13.440 --> 44:16.040
           # I love him

44:16.040 --> 44:20.040
     # Because he's wonderful

44:21.720 --> 44:25.720
      # Because he's just...

44:28.400 --> 44:32.400
           # My Bill. #

44:36.160 --> 44:37.400
Good night.

44:37.400 --> 44:40.320
Oh, Dr Auschlander.
We just got the most bizarre call.

44:40.320 --> 44:44.160
A sanitarium in New Orleans called
to say that two people escaped

44:44.160 --> 44:46.720
and were headed to Boston
to look for a friend.

44:46.720 --> 44:50.200
They asked us to check the psych
ward for a Lucinda and Ramsay...

44:50.200 --> 44:51.760
something or other.

44:51.760 --> 44:55.760
"Our revels now ended.
These our actors, as I told you,

44:56.920 --> 45:00.920
"were all spirits and are melted
into air. Into thin air."

45:02.080 --> 45:04.000
He belongs in a sanitarium.

